Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:04.09,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alibis, codes, tricks, deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:06.09,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The mysterious Black Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:07.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's stage is a big mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:09.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A soon-to-be bride has a lot on her mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:13.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what's with all the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a festival goin' on or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shibuya's always like this on weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There sure are a lotta people around, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:02:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like being at the big Tenjin festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yer right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or like the cherry blossom viewing at the Japan Mint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You call me from Tokyo Station,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,announcing that you're in town and you want a sightseeing tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so stingy! You weren't doin' nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got some business here,\Nand I've never looked around Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mom's classmate's son's wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mom was gonna attend it herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she dropped a {\i1}takoyaki{\i0} grill\Non her foot and broke a bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in her place, you're attending\Nthe wedding with Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's just tagging along!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to come,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but Heiji's mother {\i1}begged{\i0} me to look after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right. You were all giddy about shopping in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know this great shop onâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already researched the stores I wanna hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think it'll look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not? You're super-cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you like it, you'd better buy it,\Nor someone else'll get it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeesh! What's takin' Heiji and the others so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after they nagged {\i1}us{\i0} about spending too much time in the shops!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}me{\i0}, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wearin' the same kind of shirt as Heiji, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two were both wearin' black, collared shirts when you came to Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you picked 'em out beforehand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about tacky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so lame for a couple to wear matching clothes, don't ya think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It grosses me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! We're in the middle of town, ya know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There! Now I'm wearing a different shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're... a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the Meiji Temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha! Pray for your thighs to get thinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut that trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:43.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, you took off that shirt your mother gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it got a little sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that you, Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd see {\i1}you{\i0} up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be at the house by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the butler of the family\Nmy mom's classmate is marryin' into!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:18.15,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Akio Shigematsu (51)\NMorizono Family Butler
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you. I'm Shigematsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what're you doing at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Escorting the young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to look around Tokyo before the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaede{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who'll be marrying young master Kikuhito tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:39.30,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kaede Katagiri (22)\NKikuhito Morizono's fiancÃ©e
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Kaede Katagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But shouldn't her fiancÃ© be showing her around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I invited him to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my fault. I wanted to go to Tokyo Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young master has been afraid of heights since he was small.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? What did you pray for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be blessed with children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With children?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasn't the look I saw on her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A girl getting married has a lot on her mind, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. Wedding blues, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did those two get all chummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This house is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hasn't changed since I visited it as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we can just drop in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! If you have the time,\Nyou should have dinner here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Don't be so rude in front of the guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:50.45,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yuji Sakuraba (23)\NMorizono Family Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The master's cat ran away and climbbed a tree again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you must be my little brother's princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're the daughter\Nof the chairman of a big company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to beat the rules of\Nthis family into your bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er... okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm his sister, Yurie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:26.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yurie Morizono (28)\NEldest Morizono Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm usually abroad, so I won't\Nbe here to get on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you really are something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard you came here over and over\Nto pin my playboy brother down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:40.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, ma'am! The young master fell in love at first sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not what you told me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, you arranged this marriage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father may reward you for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here's the famous detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mouri, at your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's certainly an honor\Nto dine with a man like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the honor's all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to have a yearning\Nto become a detective myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:19.12,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mikio Morizono\NHead of the Morizono family
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how does it feel to be called one of\Nthe greatest forensic minds of our era?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it sure is surprising that all\Nmy cases are solved so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dream? You've got that right, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you bring the camera?\NWe should get a picture of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'll need you to drop by my room later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've done so much for my son's marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:08:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My cat seems to have disappeared again. Could you have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a very skittish cat.\NIt was attached to my wife, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:23.56,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kikuhito Morizono (26)\NEldest Morizono Son
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother passed away four years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in an unfortunate road accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. This is my son, Kikuhito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy your day in Tokyo, my honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Honey"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll drop by your office after the wedding tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see you tomorrow. Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a sigh of relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time I'm with him, I get dragged into a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... right! That guy's a magnet for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The window on the third floor!\NSomebody broke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, keep an eye on that window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha! Just in case, go call Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez! It's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys! Where's Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the problem!\NHe's been missing for a while now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoot! He's the one with all the keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Better break down the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It continues into the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that scream just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's been a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r} is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! This has gotta be a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaede{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you guys doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Kaede{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've called for the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stay where you are until they arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This side's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So is this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang on, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't start tinkering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've been watchin' this window till now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't see anyone come out this way, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Didn't I tell you to stay put?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r} is the only person who had all the keys to the house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a spare key for this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:13:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone has a spare key to their private rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for rooms we don't often use, like this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} kept all the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'm gonna have to test something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Test?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key to the door we just broke through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the key to this door...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is somewhere on this keyring...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ya get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had to break down the door 'cause it was locked, right, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The room where the body was found has two locked windows...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and nobody escaped through the window in the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the only key to this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was in the inner pocket of Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r}'s jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. There's another answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a locked-room murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could have locked the door himself and committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'd find some sort of weapon next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body has obviously been stabbed in the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So somebody, somehow, disappeared from this room, along with the murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoever did it, it's going to cause problems with the wedding tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Kikuhito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't possibly have the wedding now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, big sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim isn't a member of the Morizono family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:15:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to bother to change my honeymoon schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know he was with the house for a long time, and I'm sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we spent a fortune on the ceremony tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would be happier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Kikuhito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man has {\i1}died{\i0}, and that's all you've got to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} lost his parents at a young age, and Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was like a father to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show a little human feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was the person who arranged this marriage in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} worked hard at the company I'm putting you in charge of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you be so disrespectful to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never raise a hand against a member of the family you serve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From now on, restrain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yurie, I'll need you to contact Kaede{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell them the wedding has been postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did that man just move?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that cat was at the scene of the crime all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad cats can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She seems close to that cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yurie is the spitting image of my late wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cat only comes near my son or me when we feed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master! The police are here! Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that. I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was riding with my wife when our car crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only injured my leg, but my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morizono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true that your butler's been murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will your son's wedding tomorrow be cancelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are rumors of bribery in your son's company!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that have anything to do with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Save the questions for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Megure, from the Metro Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already heard the details of this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from that walking bad-luck charm over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on. I'm not bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cases just happen to call the name of the great Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A locked-room murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both the door and the windows were locked,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nobody escaped through the window in the next room,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the murder weapon's missing. Which means it's a locked-room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A locked room...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know there was a body in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That window suddenly shattered while I was just outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.76,0:18:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We ran up and knocked on the door, but no one answered,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:39.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we forced our way in, and found the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's premature to call this a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim could have stabbed himself in the chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then thrown the knife through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That ain't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We looked at the window right after it broke,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we didn't see anything come flyin' out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if he'd chucked the weapon out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there'd be more blood around the window, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look at the bloodstains! The body was obviously dragged to where it's lyin' now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The window must've been broken by accident during the struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or somebody saw us outside and used this chair to break the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they {\i1}wanted{\i0} to draw our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the body was discovered, an hour and a half ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,most of the household servants were having dinner in the kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and discussing the wedding plans when the murder took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only people who don't have clear alibis seem to be these five.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be talking to each of you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, I'd like you to submit to a quick body search, then wait in your rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officers, go over the house and grounds with a fine-tooth comb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon must be {\i1}somewhere{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want you to find it at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many have ya got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I noticed four suspicious points, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, there's the missing murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer took the trouble to create a locked-room scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leaving the weapon behind would've made it look more like a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there are those bloodstains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd the killer drag the body into the next room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Third, why was the light on in the room with the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And most suspicious of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- The cat!\N- The cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I thought I had one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me help in the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! You have to stay in your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can't sit idly by!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it the hell off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell that every time you do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you just cause more trouble for the Morizono family?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your place, servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm... fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They match.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not your clothes! The pendants!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pendants?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it come off his neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Kaede{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} are wearin' the same pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:21:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right. It can't be a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've found another piece of this puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's give it a try using the next balcony over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.18,0:23:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give what a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.86,0:23:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to find out if this escape method is really possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:23:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who's gonna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something stuck in that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.54,0:24:15.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Bag
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:22.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, it's the Great Detectives of the East and West again!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.20,0:24:24.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we've got to arrest the killer, or else!
